  "description": "<p>📣 PART-TIME SERVICE CREW WANTED (CNY PERIOD) 🧧<br /></p><p>🍽 Company: Tai Er</p><p>📍Location: Multiple Locations</p><p>📅 Working Dates: 16 – 19 Feb</p><p>⏰ Operating Hours: 10:30am – 10:30pm</p><p>🕒 Working Hours: Flexible, depends on availability & schedule</p><p>💰 Salary: Up to $19.50 / hour</p><p>👕 Role: Service Crew</p><p></p><p>✨ Job Scope:</p><p></p><p>💫Provide excellent customer service to all guests</p><p>💫Set up restaurant according to SOPs</p><p>💫Serve food and beverages</p><p>💫Clear and sanitise tables</p><p></p><p>✅ Requirements:</p><p>💪🏻Cheerful and positive attitude</p><p>💪🏻Able to work in a fast-paced restaurant environment</p><p>💪🏻Prior waiter/waitress experience is a plus</p><p>💪🏻Basic conversational and reading Mandarin is a plus</p><p></p><p>📌 Great opportunity to earn extra during the CNY period!<br /><br />Interested? Apply now! <br /><br />Or email your resume to pamela.lim.taier@gmail.com</p>",
